{"tid":1743892,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【政治表態】本人堅決反對香港獨立","createTime":"2019-11-21T12:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T15:56:35.000Z","uid":125976,"like":39,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"20c70eab941b9388d29844e48fc20d84a52ce6ac","tid":1743892,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:10:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港係美國第51州</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你話而家唔係？<br />\n好快會係<br />\n就算名義上唔係<br />\n本質上都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有美國<br />\n我哋唔洗再俾人蝦<br />\n香港唔需要獨立<br />\n香港需要國家嘅保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋國家有地球三大證券交易所：<br />\n- 芝加哥交易所<br />\n- 紐約交易所<br />\n- 香港交易所<br />\n<br />\n我哋國家有地球最完善創科環境：<br />\n- 聖塔克拉拉谷園區<br />\n- 香港科學園區<br />\n<br />\n我哋國家有地球上最頂尖嘅學府：<br />\n- 麻省理工學院<br />\n- 香港理工學院<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港加油，美國加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"720fbb44dd1323e95fb852c1e676de7442076d1f","tid":1743892,"uid":340761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:13:38.000Z","msg":"PolyU同MIT？ 算了 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係比較期待Campus shooting多d"},{"pid":"6b51915bc6a630d40eeaace77ec5fefe2fe4a075","tid":1743892,"uid":250511,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"發完夢就醒啦"},{"pid":"47b61af5c32808a00a526dde9a382c5d3a9683c6","tid":1743892,"uid":125976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b51915bc6a630d40eeaace77ec5fefe2fe4a075","tid":1743892,"uid":250511,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"發完夢就醒啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"我從來都冇發你哋嗰啲「夢」<br />\n但好快你哋會知道<br />\n𠵱個係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c2133ce07a1b358b6a3177e6c6881dd733f72f","tid":1743892,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"戰役過後，痛定思痛，認清現實，重新出發(抗爭五部曲-前言)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742018</a>"},{"pid":"553d872322bf557ea91de21f5e2c1972f7e59ef3","tid":1743892,"uid":182624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:31:27.000Z","msg":"埋土不了，暴大is ok"},{"pid":"604afff085af55745820a9770f684b5de4042c0f","tid":1743892,"uid":325556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"720fbb44dd1323e95fb852c1e676de7442076d1f","tid":1743892,"uid":340761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:13:38.000Z","msg":"PolyU同MIT？ 算了 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係比較期待Campus shooting多d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:35:02.000Z","msg":"美屬香港咁人口密集，每日兩單差唔多"},{"pid":"a388e07f06a48351b1867ec298ee69a5db7bbbbd","tid":1743892,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f8abda681d2dc7acfdcb89778dcf5eacceecdd","tid":1743892,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"San Jose (CA)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgYMYwV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgYMYwV.jpg&h=52980705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHKSTP (HK)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7HxJ0Ld.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7HxJ0Ld.jpg&h=6e7e7261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實兩度都幾靚，當年 HK 割讓咗俾中共真係晒咗